      <title>香港迪士尼乐园过山车上十二人获救</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/twelve-trapped-rollercoaster-hong-kong-disneyland-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[警方和消防部门在部署了数十名人员到现场后表示，周三下午香港迪士尼乐园的过山车停止运行后，有十二人从该过山车中被救出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/twelve-trapped-rollercoaster-hong-kong-disneyland-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 08:35:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>路透调查：新兴市场货币短期内将稳步上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/emerging-market-currencies-gain-steadily-near-term-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透对外汇策略师的一项调查发现，随着美联储大幅降息的预期减弱，大多数新兴市场货币兑美元汇率在未来几个月将难以收复今年的损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/emerging-market-currencies-gain-steadily-near-term-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 07:50:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
