      <title>珠宝商潘多拉 (Pandora) 今年迄今销售额“健康”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/pandora-sets-2024-organic-revenue-growth-target-after-strong-run-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的珠宝制造商潘多拉 (Pandora) 周三表示，自今年年初以来，其业绩“健康”，销售额实现高个位数增长，并在强劲表现后宣布了股票回购计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/pandora-sets-2024-organic-revenue-growth-target-after-strong-run-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 06:51:54 GMT</pubDate>
