      <title>巴布亚新几内亚将在马拉佩访问期间向澳大利亚保证安全关系</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/png-assures-australia-security-ties-leader-marape-arrives-visit-2024-02-07/</link>
